OMNISTUDIO
Add a Customer Story to a Page with the Story-SLDS Component

Before You Begin
Configure the objects displayed in the customer story. See Configure the Objects Displayed in a Customer Story.
Activate the story-slds component. See Activate the Story-SLDS Component.

To add the story-slds component to a Lightning page:
Open an Account, Contact, Household, or Opportunity record and click Edit Page from the Setup menu.
Drag the story-slds component from the list of Custom components in the Components pane onto the canvas.
Click Save.

Add a New Object to the Story-SLDS Component
Clone and modify the story-slds card layout to add a new story object to the Customer Story timeline.
The Vlocity Customer Story displays a timeline of all interactions with a customer in a single, chronological feed.

Activate the Story-SLDS Component
To display a Customer Story on a Lightning or Community page, the story-slds component must be active.
